    "causal_summary": "The current ablation path can report invalid Recall@20 values because the benchmark still allows chunk-ID scoring on the CLI path, live token-budget and confidence truncation can cut results below `K=20`, and the active database may not match the parent-memory ID universe encoded in `ground-truth.json`. Those failures produced the misleading `0.0101` baseline collapse and made the FTS5 0.3 retune impossible to judge fairly.",
